ger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI have been sent as close to the Hour as these\u00a0two,\u201d and he held up his two fingers together. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6138, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2950 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1043,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/09\/24\/cuts-off-family-no-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":34923,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Rahim: Whoever cuts off family will not enter Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 24, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Jubayr ibn Mut'im reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe one who severs his family ties will not enter Paradise.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5984, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2556 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064f\u0637\u0652\u0639\u0650\u0645\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7537,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/03\/family-ties-increase-wealth-life\/","url_meta":{"origin":34923,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Rahim: Good relations with family increase wealth, extend life","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 3, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik\u00a0reported: The\u00a0Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever is pleased to have his provision expanded and his life span extended, let him keep good relations with his family.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2067, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2557 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42192,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2024\/08\/28\/love-rasul-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":34923,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Muhammad: Love for the Prophet is true faith","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 28, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBy the One in whose hand is my soul, none of you have faith until I am more beloved to him than his parents and his children.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 14 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15496,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/29\/travel-quickly-return-family\/","url_meta":{"origin":34923,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Travel: Return to family as fast as you can","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 29, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTravel is a piece of torment. It prevents one of you from eating, drinking, and sleeping. When he has finished his purpose, let him quickly return to his family.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1804, Sahih Muslim 1927 Grade: Muttafaqun\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15500,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/29\/startle-surprise-scare-family\/","url_meta":{"origin":34923,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Travel: Do not surprise family in the night","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 29, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf one of you is absent for a long time while traveling, let him not startle his family in the night upon his return.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5244, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 715 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/34923","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collect